Save Time with Content Record Cloning in Your Enhanced CMS Workspace
Preview Custom Content Types in Enhanced CMS Workspaces
Preview CMS Content as a Guest or Authenticated User
Secure Linked Sources in Salesforce CMS Content with Trusted URLs
Add an API Name to New Enhanced CMS Workspaces and Content

You can preview custom content types on your enhanced LWR site without leaving your enhanced CMS workspace. Preview content before or after publishing, and switch between desktop and mobile views.

This applies to enhanced CMS workspaces in Lightning Experience for Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions. Add the site as a channel, create a CMS Content page, and click Preview on the content detail page.
title: Enhanced CMS Workspaces and Custom Content Types
